cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "VS2: A Reproducible LLM-DAG Pipeline for Bibliometric Entity Matching"
abstract: >
  VS2 is a reproducible entity-matching pipeline for bibliometric data
  exported from the Scopus UI. It resolves Author Name Disambiguation (AND)
  and Affiliation Name Normalisation (AIN) using a multi-stage DAG with
  optional LLM verification.
authors:
